  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Tripura</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Tripura experiences monsoon (May-September), cool autumn (October-November), mild winter (December-February) and warm spring (March-April). October to March offers ideal weather with comfortable temperatures, clear skies and excellent visibility for exploring historical sites and natural attractions.</p>
